<br>
there is absolutely no difference in performance. Not in mes, not in charm. None. if you want to believe that cha helps you mes/charm better, go right ahead, I want to believe it, too. I can take off half my gear, and still have 255 cha. If high cha affects charm/mes, i would be totally awesome.<br>
<br>
