<br>
Of course, int/cha balancing is not the case now, as enchanters are able to get 200 int/cha quite easily. I would like verant to re-enable this stat, IF it's disabled. If it's disabled, it's a totally useless stat for anything, except for selling, and even then it's capped at 150. What reward do i get for having 255 cha? None. <br>
