<br>
Charms can break after 1 second at 200+ cha as much as they can at 100-<br>
Mezzes are set duration.<br>
Resist checks are on magic, not your standing charisma.<br>
<br>
The only reason a chanter needs good cha is if he/she does jewel craft, which is the most common class for the job.  And that only needs to be 105 with amiable faction.  Or 150+ with Indifferent faction.<br>
<br>
